| `Tests/Automation/status.lua` | DwarfSpec installed host entry point; move under `dwarfspec.*`. |
| `Tests/Automation/fixtures/cover_screen.lua` | Generic DwarfSpec self-test fixture; move and remove tooltip-specific prose from its generic covering-screen role. |
